  "title": "Chinese Preschool Teacher",
  "description": "<p>Our warm and happy preschool is looking for passionate and dedicated Teacher to join us in our next leap!</p>\n<p>Conveniently located in the heart of the CBD, opposite Telok Ayer Mrt and within walking distance to Raffles Place &amp; Tanjong Pagar MRT.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive remuneration and staff welfare benefits</li>\n  <li>Ample opportunities for Career Progression</li>\n  <li>Up to 21 days of Annual Leave, 1 day of Birthday Leave, 4 days of study leave</li>\n  <li>Low Teacher-Children Ratio</li>\n  <li>Friendly and Conducive working environment</li>\n  <li>Comprehensive HQ training for all teachers</li>\n  <li>Strong Curriculum team and mentorship programs available</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Certificate / Fundamental in Early Childhood Care &amp; Education</li>\n  <li>Creative and inspiring with loving energy</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Contact us at sg.cpscecilst.principal@mindchamps.org if you think you are ready for the next upgrade in your career!</p>",
